2.6.6 默认使用是netty4，但是依赖的jar 是 netty3， 启动时报错，请看清我的问题再关闭issue

解决方案:
去掉application，将上面api调用泛化接口改为以下代码

 ```
@Override
    public void executor(CheckCallBack checkCallBack, Map<String, Object> params) {
        try {
            RegistryConfig registry = new RegistryConfig();
            registry.setAddress(ADDRESS_PREFIX + checkCallBack.getInvokeAddress());
            registry.setCheck(false);
            ReferenceConfig<GenericService> reference = new ReferenceConfig<>();
            reference.setInterface(checkCallBack.getInvokeMode());
            reference.setRegistry(registry);
            reference.setGeneric(true);
            reference.setOwner(checkCallBack.getCreater());
            GenericService genericService = reference.get();
            Object result = genericService.$invoke(checkCallBack.getInvokeStrategy(), new String[]{Map.class.getName()}, new Object[]{params});
            log.info("DubboStrategy.dubbo.resutl:{}", result);
        } catch (IllegalStateException e) {
            log.error("DubboStrategy.dubbo.error:{}", e.getMessage());
            throw new BcpException(String.format("dubbo接口调用失败,ERROR:%s", e.getLocalizedMessage()));
        }
    }
```

